== Slide Decks

Training slide decks for presentations and workshops.

=== Onboarding & Roles
- link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/IPMC/index.html[IPMC Onboarding] — orientation on the IPMC’s oversight role and responsibilities  
- link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/mentors/index.html[Mentor Onboarding] — overview of mentoring practices and expectations  
- link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/PPMC/index.html[PPMC Onboarding] — explains the role of the Podling PMC and community leadership  
- link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/committers/index.html[Committer Onboarding] — guidance for new committers on rights and responsibilities  

=== Governance & Decision-Making
- link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/Governance/index.html[Governance in Practice] — how ASF governance works day to day  
- link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/VotingAndConsensus/index.html[Voting and Consensus in Practice] — understanding how Apache communities make decisions  
- link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/incubator-releases/index.html[Incubator Releases] — training on ASF release process, requirements, and policies  

=== Community & Values
- link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/ASFvalues/index.html[ASF Values] — introduction to the core cultural values of the ASF  
- link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/CommunityBuilding/index.html[Community Building in Practice] — building and sustaining healthy, diverse communities  

=== Policies & Compliance
- link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/VendorNeutrality/index.html[Vendor Neutrality] — why balanced governance keeps Apache projects healthy and independent  
- link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/BrandingIdentity/index.html[Branding & Identity] — guidance on name use, logo policy, and protecting ASF trademarks  

NOTE: These slide decks are hosted in the ASF Training GitHub repository (link:https://github.com/apache/training/tree/develop/content/Apache/Incubator[Incubator Training Slides]) and include extensive speaker notes. You’re encouraged to use, adapt, and build on them for your own presentations.
